						<p>On an image of Gaṇapati in the Āñjanēya temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1033, Khara, Kārttika śu. 1, Thursday = 1111 A.D., October 5.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the setting up of an image at Aḍigappu by Dōchama, son of Divākara Peggaḍa, who is described as <hi rend="italic">samasta-vishayādhikāra-saṁpanna.</hi></p>						

